{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "9.0",
      "line_index": 9,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c91c61c7",
      "speaker": "信徒A",
      "ja": "コハル様～！　どうか我々の教会へ来てください！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "11.0",
      "line_index": 11,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "22234091",
      "speaker": "信徒B",
      "ja": "コハル神様～！　お怒りをお鎮めくださいませ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.1",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1b0c788b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ああもう、襲ってきてるわけじゃないから反撃しにくい……！　どうしよう！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.1",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "35d2c113",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "睡眠命令弾で、危険そうな相手は眠らせていますが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5eb900f8",
      "speaker": "信徒C",
      "ja": "ああ、これが神の御業……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "987c78d2",
      "speaker": "信徒D",
      "ja": "コハル様の眷属の方♥　私にも、その御業を体感させてくださいっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6a1389e9",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "むしろ勢いが増しているような……というか、眷属とは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.1",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7f5021bb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（うっ、神様呼ばわりされるのも大概だけど、王女様に対してそんな扱い……気まずい！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.1",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6707fa4e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "どこかから、抜けられたりしませんかね！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.1",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "993c6bad",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "私もそう考えましたが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.1",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d3ec9b4a",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "おっほっほ！　無理でしょう？　これだけの信徒の壁をくぐり抜けるのは！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.1",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4a01cdbc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ラト……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.1",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f6b6b801",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "\"鍵拝教\"の信徒数はこの街でも随一！　囲んでしまえば逃げ場なんてありませんよぉ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.1",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7a969c70",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "……ま、まあ。天に還るとかは後でなんとかするとして。まずは捕まえなければ始まりません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.1",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "790b4563",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "先程とは香を変えて、洗脳部屋……ではなく赦しの間に入っていただければ、考えもお変わりになるはずです！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.1",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "12cec062",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "洗脳部屋って言った！？　今！　やっぱり危ない部屋だったんじゃないの！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.1",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1f13d583",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（ああもう、{G_PlayerName}は大丈夫かしら……！？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.1",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "360c5fc1",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "……困りましたね。非殺傷兵器では、これ以上打つ手がありません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.1",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "689c4be1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "す、すみません巻き込んじゃって……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.1",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "38435df9",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "いいえ。それに、私は……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.1",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "162423f1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "っ！？　あれ、グレアさん！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d939e8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一瞬でグレアの姿は消え去った。あたりを見回しても、逃げた様子、隠れた様子は無い。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.1",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f8485ac7",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "い、一体どうやって……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d57ad3b",
      "speaker": "信徒E",
      "ja": "コハル様……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.1",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9417274",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "っ…………！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1e48261",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こちらの抵抗が弱まり、信徒に距離を詰められる。信徒に次々と腕を掴まれ、振り払っても倍の腕に掴まれる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.0",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29f2bc7c",
      "speaker": "信徒F",
      "ja": "恐ろしいことなどございません、こちらへ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.1",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a3b4266c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（この人たち、心の底から善意であたしを連れて行こうとしてる……！　こ、怖い……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.1",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7c69f58d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1241d48",
      "speaker": "？？？",
      "ja": "者ども、控えよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "de78675c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "え…………？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "589507b7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "街に響く声。声の主を探し、誰もが視線を迷わせる。腕を掴む腕達の力が、大きく緩んだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12b972ad",
      "speaker": "信徒G",
      "ja": "あそこだ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c1177c6a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "信徒の１人が天を指差す。その先には……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.1",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7f45a62e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "…………はああっ！！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1feed2c7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "地に伏し、我が声を……聞くのだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a9da43fe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "天からゆっくりと降りてくる{G_PlayerName}。……目を擦って改めて見上げるコハルだが、眼の前に広がる景色は変わることはない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21b4261b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "周りの信徒たちは地にひれ伏し、空に浮く{G_PlayerName}を見上げている。そのうち{G_PlayerName}は地面に降り立った。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bcd51eff",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そのまま聞くがいい。コハル、こちらへ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.1",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9a738f5e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（ちょ……ちょっと、これどういうこと！？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "19425e60",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "我らは確かに汝らが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.0",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1650a9d0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……思うように、神の使いである",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.1",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f5b1b8ff",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（……台本見てる！？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7057605",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "見れば、{G_PlayerName}の手には文章が墨で書かれており、時折目線をやりながらそれを読み上げているようだった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7aad4ed4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "されど、我らは汝らの助けなく天へと還ることが出来る。汝らに命ずる",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78b41de",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……我らは今から天へと還るが、それを妨げず、伏したまま見届けるが良い",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.1",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fbcc9939",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ええっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "17cf497",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに、空から降りてくる大きな影。アポロの宇宙船本体が、空から街に大きな影を作っていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "19b33d73",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（行くぞ）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.1",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bf51c1d3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "え、あ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3300a319",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは{G_PlayerName}にしがみつくような形で、上空の宇宙船へと吸い込まれていった……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.1",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e353593e",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "な……な……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.1",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ca09a740",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "なんなのですかあれはっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.1",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "41f23f31",
      "speaker": "グレメイン",
      "ja": "やはり……天から訪れた神族の方々は、長くこの世界にはいられないのですね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.1",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5b933cb8",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "グレメインっ！　まさか、貴方がまた余計なことを……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.1",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b01b38ea",
      "speaker": "グレメイン",
      "ja": "とんでもございません、天の使いに対して矮小なわたくしが何を出来ましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.1",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f196616b",
      "speaker": "ラト",
      "ja": "くううっ……！　わたくしは全部わかっているのですから！　騙されませんからね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.1",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "de4446e9",
      "speaker": "メイズ",
      "ja": "わお。ド派手に帰っていったね～、あれって法律違反じゃないのかな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.1",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "22fadbac",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "……宇宙船、だとは思っていないので問題無いでしょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.1",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "33065a55",
      "speaker": "メイズ",
      "ja": "あはは、あたし達もああやって帰っちゃう～！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "192.1",
      "line_index": 192,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8df9912c",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "必要無いでしょう……視察は済んだし、戻りますよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.1",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b663407e",
      "speaker": "メイズ",
      "ja": "オッケー♪　お疲れお疲れー♪　じゃ、戻ろ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.1",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cb20c01e",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "……メイズ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "200.1",
      "line_index": 200,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bfb20513",
      "speaker": "メイズ",
      "ja": "ん？　何、グレア？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "202.1",
      "line_index": 202,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cc50222c",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "204.1",
      "line_index": 204,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "81738b5b",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "なんでも、ないです……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.1",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3f9758ed",
      "speaker": "メイズ",
      "ja": "そう？　早く行こ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.1",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5c9b1c13",
      "speaker": "グレア",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "233.1",
      "line_index": 233,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f5fd0def",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "もう、心臓止まるかと思ったわよ！　もっとスムーズに助けられないわけ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "235.0",
      "line_index": 235,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1e4771a3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "す、すまん！　グレメインさんの提案でああするしか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "237.1",
      "line_index": 237,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b3d72ca3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "グレメインさんが？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "239.0",
      "line_index": 239,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b29fa896",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、水を探しててグレメインさんに会ったから、案内してもらってたんだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "252.0",
      "line_index": 252,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "770a97e0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハルが追われてる……！　助けないと！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "254.1",
      "line_index": 254,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "edaa9fe8",
      "speaker": "グレメイン",
      "ja": "お待ち下さい。この状況では普通に助けるのは難しいかと",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.0",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "da8056e2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "で、でも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "258.1",
      "line_index": 258,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2e17c936",
      "speaker": "グレメイン",
      "ja": "幸い、別に殺されようとしてるわけでもありません。時間をかけて、確実に助けましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "260.1",
      "line_index": 260,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fa1f193c",
      "speaker": "グレメイン",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}さんが乗ってきた宇宙船。ありますよね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "275.1",
      "line_index": 275,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "665f3440",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "グレメインさん、宇宙船知ってたの！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "277.1",
      "line_index": 277,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "da46b084",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "この星の……崇姫って呼ばれてる人だけは、宇宙技術の存在を知ってるの。……伝え忘れちゃってた、ね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.1",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "36dea7e8",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それで、ルミナ様のお力を使いながら透明なワイヤーで機械士を吊るしたというわけです",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "281.1",
      "line_index": 281,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e54c2d0a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……ってことは、グレメインさん、最初のほうは知っててからかってたのね！？　も～！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "283.0",
      "line_index": 283,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7f8217d9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "案外いたずら心がある人なのかもな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "285.1",
      "line_index": 285,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6eda8eae",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "全く、不調なルミナ様にご迷惑をおかけするとは！　機械士も男ならあれくらいの人混み小指一本で消し飛ばしなさい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "287.0",
      "line_index": 287,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e48c96a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どんな男だ！　……ルミナに迷惑かけたのは申し訳ないけどな。ごめん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "289.1",
      "line_index": 289,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a7f06015",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "う、ううん！　全然……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "291.1",
      "line_index": 291,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a5b1e208",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "まあ、騒ぎを起こしていたおかげでわたくしは物資調達がすんなり終わりましたけれども",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "293.1",
      "line_index": 293,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "54905a72",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "け、結局雫が買ってきてたのね……ごめんなさい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "295.1",
      "line_index": 295,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6030c7aa",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "とんでもございませんっ♥　もとよりわたくしの役目ですもの、心優しいコハル様にはいつも感謝しておりますわ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "297.0",
      "line_index": 297,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c424ee71",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "差別だ……疲れたし、部屋に戻るか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "299.1",
      "line_index": 299,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "22728c8a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうね。もうずーっとお腹空いちゃってて大変だったわ！　部屋で何か食べましょ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "316.1",
      "line_index": 316,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f3bf2c47",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "318.0",
      "line_index": 318,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a2b28761",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "320.1",
      "line_index": 320,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c0333048",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（洗脳部屋じゃ変なとこ見せちゃった……かも知れないし、気まずいわね……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "322.1",
      "line_index": 322,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a5a73cf6",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ね、ねえ？　そういえば今回の星じゃ機械は殆ど無かったわね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "324.0",
      "line_index": 324,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6478d4fc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え？　ああ、そうだな。そういう技術レベルはそこまで高く無かったのかもな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "326.1",
      "line_index": 326,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d763f969",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あれだけキレイな建物作ってるんだから、何かしら機械は使ってそうだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "328.1",
      "line_index": 328,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4683b70",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そういえば……{G_PlayerName}が今まで作った機械の中で、一番のお気に入りって何？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "330.0",
      "line_index": 330,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "375783e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お気に入り？　一番の？　そうだな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "332.1",
      "line_index": 332,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "97f6e21a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（多分、大事にしてた銃か……ルミナのために作った光る爆弾とか、かな）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "334.0",
      "line_index": 334,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e2f9e5cd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "プラネタリウムだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "336.1",
      "line_index": 336,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7299f06e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "えっ？　プラネタリウム？　……なんで？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.0",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "138ffd49",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんでって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "340.0",
      "line_index": 340,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "798130f3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……ほら、プラネタリウム作った時さ、コハルに見せただろ。テントの中で試運転してさ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "342.1",
      "line_index": 342,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a8b49418",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うん……覚えてるけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "344.0",
      "line_index": 344,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e42c3636",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今まで銃の失敗作とかガタガタ動く人形とか見せても、お前の反応ってあんまり良くなかったんだよ。でも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "346.0",
      "line_index": 346,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "964d52e4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "プラネタリウムを見せた時は、お前があんまり喜ぶもんだからさ。今でもあの機械が一番作って良かったなーって思うんだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "348.1",
      "line_index": 348,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ee748b9f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "350.1",
      "line_index": 350,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d955050b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そ、そーなんだー。なるほどねー。じゃ、お疲れ様",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "353.0",
      "line_index": 353,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "65ba1d28",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは早口でそう言うと、自分の部屋へと小走りで入っていった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "355.0",
      "line_index": 355,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "316336d4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんだよその反応は！　自分で言わせたんだろ！",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
